k/programmes/b00mjlxv|accessdate=May 30, 2013}}</ref>\n* ''[[Beyond Belief: Fact or Fiction]]''<ref name=BeyondBeliefChiller>{{cite web|title=Beyond Belief on Chiller|url=http://www.chillertv.com/shows/beyond_belief/|accessdate=May 30, 2013}}</ref>\n* ''[[Law & Order: Special Victims Unit]]'' (4 episodes aired for one night, all were related to [[serial killers]])<ref name=LawOrderNBC>{{cite web|title=NBC Law & Order: Special Victims Unit|url=http://www.nbc.com/law-and-order-special-victims-unit/|accessdate=May 30, 2013}}</ref><ref name=LawOrderCTV>{{cite web|title=CTV Law & Order: Special Victims Unit|url=http://www.ctv.ca/LawAndOrderSVU.aspx|accessdate=May 30, 2013}}</ref>\n* ''[[Heroes (American TV series)|Heroes]]'' (2006\u201310) (repurposed airing, Fridays at 7PM Eastern, of the NBC series; started airing Friday, September 29, 2006)<ref name=HeroesNBC>{{cite web|title=Heroes on NBC|url=http://www.nbc.com/heroes/|accessdate=May 30, 2013}}</ref>\n* ''[[Surface (TV series)|Surface]]'' (2005\u201306)\n* ''[[Passions]]'' (1999\u20132008)<ref name=PassionsEnd>{{cite web|title=NBC Passions soap opera moved to direcTV, cancelled|url=http://tvseriesfinale.com/tv-show/passions-nbc-soap-headed-for-directv/|accessdate=May 30, 2013}}</ref>\n* ''[[Chuck (TV series)|Chuck]]'' (2007\u201312)<ref name=ChuckFans>{{cite web|title=Chuck fan site|url=http://chucktv.net/|accessdate=May 30, 2013}}</ref><ref name=ChuckYvonne>{{cite news|title=Chuck star Yvonne Strahovski interview with Huffington Post|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/morgan-glennon/yvonne-strahovski-discuss_b_3329491.html|accessdate=May 30, 2013 | first=Morgan|last=Glennon|date=May 24, 2013}}</ref>\n* ''[[Lost (TV series)|Lost]]'' (2004\u201310)\n* ''[[Spartacus (TV series)|Spartacus]]'' (2010\u201313) (originally aired on [[Starz]])\n\n==TZGZ programming==\n{{Main|TZGZ}}\n\n===Current programming===\n====Original====\n* ''[[Happy Tree Friends]]'' (2020-present), co-production with [[Working Title Films|WT 2 Produc